dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents dams and weirs in Guinea-Bissau. The Global MapGuinea-Bissau version 2 was developed to update Global Map Guinea-Bissau version 1 based on Global Map Specifications version 2.1.Global Map data were developed under the cooperation of National Geospatial Information Authorities (NGIAs) of respective countries and regions.
